org.apache.flink.runtime.deployment

类 InputChannelDeploymentDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.deployment.InputChannelDeploymentDescriptor
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class InputChannelDeploymentDescriptor
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Deployment descriptor for a single input channel instance.

    Each input channel consumes a single subpartition. The index of the subpartition to consume is part of the InputGateDeploymentDescriptor as it is the same for each input channel of the respective input gate.

    另请参阅:
    InputChannel, SingleInputGate, 序列化表格
